Package: tvrmst
Type: Package
Title: Time-Varying RMST from Survival Matrices (Model-Agnostic)
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: c(
  person("Imad", "EL BADISY", role = c("aut", "cre"),
         email = "your@email.com"))
Description: Matrix-only utilities for RMST and time-varying RMST quantities
  computed from survival curves provided on a time grid. Model-agnostic accepts
  only time vector and survival matrices, returning RMST-based quantities and
  bootstrap summaries.
